      "title": "The security of the speaker is strengthened",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police sources say that the security of Mr. Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena has been strengthened.",
        "Police sources also said that in addition to the Special Task Force personnel assigned to protect the Speaker, more Special Task Force troops have been called.",
        "Police sources further say that the Special Task Force has been deployed in addition to the police."
